Method Detail

onServiceConnected

void onServiceConnected()
Callback called when service is connected. This method is called when the service is well connected to the RCS service (binding procedure successfull): this means the methods of the API may be used.

onServiceDisconnected

void onServiceDisconnected(int error)
Callback called when service has been disconnected. This method is called when the service is disconnected from the RCS service (e.g. service deactivated).

Parameters:
error - Error
